'''John Rauch''' is an [[Wikipedia:Americans|American]] colorist<ref name="Linkedin" /> who did the colors for the [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] "[[All for You]]," which was published within the [[Star Wars Tales 17|seventeenth issue]] of [[Dark Horse Comics]]' ''[[Star Wars Tales]]'' series<ref name="Tales17">{{Tales|17|All for You}}</ref> on [[October 1]], [[2003]].<ref name="Tales17date">{{DarkHorse|url=Comics/12-576/Star-Wars-Tales-17|text=Star Wars Tales #17}}</ref>

